==Болашағы==
Қазіргі уақытта әуежайда жаңа терминал салынуда. It is planned to build a new passenger terminal for international flights with six loading bridges and capacity up to 2500 passengers per hour in the nearest future. Developed infrastructure complex consisting of: a Marriott Hotel, conference halls, business center, shopping center, cinemas will be located within the territory of this terminal. 
The new terminal will be located along Kuldja road that will help to reduce traffic on the way to the airport.

